-- Hon Hai Declines to Comment on Report It's Seeking Hitachi Display Stake
-- B y   T i m   C u l p a n
-- 2010-12-28T08:52:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-28/hon-hai-declines-to-comment-on-report-it-s-seeking-hitachi-display-stake.html
Hon Hai Precision Industry Co., the
world’s largest contract manufacturer of electronics, declined
to comment on reports the company is in talks with Hitachi Ltd.
to buy a stake in Hitachi Displays Ltd.  The company doesn’t comment on cases that may be in progress
or in discussion, Taipei-based Hon Hai said in a statment to the
Taiwan stock exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tim Culpan in Taipei at 
 tculpan1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
